text:
Producer,
isn't it about time to leave?

Whoa, you're right.
Time to get ready...!
It looked like it might rain a lot on the way here──

Yeah, look, the sky is pitch black!
You'll need an umbrella.

I'm fine since I'm worried about others.
I've got a folding umbrella!

I'll──
...use the office umbrella, I guess...!
